Class LVLN

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<LeveledEntry>

    public class LVLN
extends LeveledRecord
    Leveled List. A list of entries used for spawnpoints when choosing which actor to spawn. Each entry contains a FormID of an actor, a level, and a count to spawn.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
